data.description: Welcome to your newly updated ranch in NE FDL! This home features 3 cozy bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms, perfect for anyone looking for style and comfort. The kitchen, dining room, and living room shine with new flooring, complemented by elegant wainscoting in the dining area. Enjoy the conveniences of all-new appliances and a finished basement with a rec room,  a murphy door that leads to a bonus room, offering ample space for entertaining and storage. Step outside to a maintenance-free, 6' high privacy fence encompassing a beautiful backyard with a raised deck and pergola. Complete with a 1 car garage, this home is a perfect blend of modern updates and comfortable living. Don't wait-make this dream home yours today!
